contactTemplate = GetUserAppConfig.data?.getUserAppConfig.contactTemplate.gofs;
const leadTemplate = getTemplatesForPipelines.data?.getTemplatesForPipelines['0'].pipelineItemTemplate.gofs;
const activityTemplates = getActivityTemplates2.data?.getActivityTemplates;

const getAllDetails = () => {
  const allDetails = [];

  // Retrieve details from Contact template
  contactTemplate.forEach((template) => {
    template.fields.forEach((field) => {
      if (field.systemFieldEnum !== 'CONTACT_ASSIGNEE' && field.systemFieldEnum !== 'CONTACT_ASSIGNED_ON') {
        const basicDetails = {
          section_name: template.name,
          field_id: field.fieldId,
          field_name: field.name,
          template_name: 'Contact Template'
        };
        allDetails.push(basicDetails);
      }
    });
  });

  // Retrieve details from Lead template
  leadTemplate.forEach((template) => {
    template.fields.forEach((field) => {
      if (field.systemFieldEnum !== 'LEAD_ASSIGNEE' && field.systemFieldEnum !== 'LEAD_ASSIGNED_ON') {
        const basicDetails = {
          section_name: template.name,
          field_id: field.fieldId,
          field_name: field.name,
          template_name: 'Lead Template'
        };
        allDetails.push(basicDetails);
      }
    });
  });

  // Retrieve details from Activity Templates
  activityTemplates.forEach((activity) => {
    activity.gofs.forEach((template) => {
      template.fields.forEach((field) => {
        const basicDetails = {
          section_name: template.name,
          field_id: field.fieldId,
          field_name: field.name,
          template_name: `Activity Template: ${activity.name}`
        };
        allDetails.push(basicDetails);
      });
    });
  });

  return allDetails;
};

return getAllDetails();

query GetTaskTemplates($inputArguments: TaskTemplatesParams!) {
  getTaskTemplates(params: $inputArguments) {
    __typename
    ... on TaskTemplate {
      taskTemplateId
      pipelineId
      name
      description
      color
      gofs {
        gofId
        name
        description
        orderedFieldIds
        category
        fields {
            __typename
            ... on IntegerField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              numberRangeConfig: rangeConfig {
                minValue
                maxValue
              }
              numberDefaultValue: defaultValue
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
              
            }
            ... on FloatField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              rangeConfig {
                minValue
                maxValue
              }
              floatDefaultValue: defaultValue
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on EmailField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              eamilDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on FileUploaderField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              allowedFormats
              isUnique
              fileUploaderDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on LongTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              longTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on PlainTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              plainTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on URLField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              urlDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on TimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              timeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              timerelativeDefaultValue: relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfSeconds
              }
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on DateField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              dateDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfDays
              }
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on DateTimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              dateTimeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                dateConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfDays
                }
                timeConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfSeconds
                }
              }
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on DropdownField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              options
              defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on MultiSelectField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              options
              defaultValues
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on CheckboxGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              options
              defaultValues
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on RadioGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              options
              defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on PhoneNumberField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on FieldsSelectorField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              systemFieldEnum
              options
              defaultValue
              dependentFields {
                option
                dependentFieldIds
              }
              salesTemplateId
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
          }
        }
      taskApproxDurationInMins
      orderedGofIds
      taskType
      quickEditFieldsConfig {
        fieldIds
        showPipelineItemStageQuickEditFields
      }
      iconUrl
      isDisabled
    }
    ... on TaskTemplateNotFound {
      message
      taskTemplateId
    }
    ... on TaskTemplateAccessDenied {
      message
      taskTemplateId
    }
  }
}

template.body:
mutation CreateTaskTemplate($inputArguments: CreateTaskTemplateParams!) {
  createTaskTemplate(params: $inputArguments) {
    __typename
    ... on TaskTemplate {
      taskTemplateId
      pipelineId
      name
      description
      color
      taskApproxDurationInMins
      gofs {
        gofId
        name
        description
        orderedFieldIds
        fields {
          __typename
            ... on IntegerField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              numberRangeConfig: rangeConfig {
                minValue
                maxValue
              }
              numberDefaultValue: defaultValue
              isUnique
            }
            ... on FloatField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              rangeConfig {
                minValue
                maxValue
              }
              floatDefaultValue: defaultValue
              isUnique
            }
            ... on EmailField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              eamilDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on FileUploaderField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              allowedFormats
              isUnique
              fileUploaderDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on LongTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              longTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on PlainTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              plainTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on URLField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              urlDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on TimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              timeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              timerelativeDefaultValue: relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfSeconds
              }
            }
            ... on DateField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              dateDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfDays
              }
            }
            ... on DateTimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              dateTimeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                dateConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfDays
                }
                timeConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfSeconds
                }
              }
            }
            ... on DropdownField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
            }
            ... on MultiSelectField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
            }
            ... on CheckboxGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
            }
            ... on RadioGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
            }
            ... on PhoneNumberField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              isUnique
            }
            ... on FieldsSelectorField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              dependentFields {
                option
                dependentFieldIds
              }
            }
        }
        category
      }
      taskType
      quickEditFieldsConfig {
        fieldIds
        showPipelineItemStageQuickEditFields
      }
      iconUrl
      orderedGofIds
    }
    ... on TaskTemplateNameAlreadyExists {
      message
      name
    }
    ... on PipelineNotFound {
      message
      pipelineId
    }
    ... on FieldsShouldNotBelongsToTaskTemplate {
      message
      fieldIds
    }
    ... on TaskApproxDurationInMinsShouldBePositive {
      message
    }
    ... on FieldsNotFound {
      message
      fieldIds
    }
  }
}

query GetActivityTemplates($params: ActivityTemplatesParams!) {
  getActivityTemplates(params: $params) {
    __typename
    ... on ActivityTemplate {
      activityTemplateId
      pipelineId
      name
      description
      gofs {
        gofId
        name
        description
        orderedFieldIds
        fields {
          __typename
            ... on IntegerField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              numberRangeConfig: rangeConfig {
                minValue
                maxValue

              numberDefaultValue: defaultValue
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId

            ... on FloatField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              rangeConfig {
                minValue
                maxValue

              floatDefaultValue: defaultValue
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on EmailField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              eamilDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on FileUploaderField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              allowedFormats
              isUnique
              fileUploaderDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on LongTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              longTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on PlainTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              plainTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on URLField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              urlDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on TimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              timeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              timerelativeDefaultValue: relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfSeconds
              }
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on DateField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              dateDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfDays
              }
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on DateTimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              dateTimeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                dateConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfDays
                }
                timeConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfSeconds
                }
              }
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on DropdownField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on MultiSelectField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on CheckboxGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on RadioGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on PhoneNumberField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              isUnique
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
            ... on FieldsSelectorField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              dependentFields {
                option
                dependentFieldIds
              }
              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum
              parentFieldOptions {
                parentFieldId
                options
              }
              referenceId
            }
        }
        category
      }
      referenceId
      orderedGofIds
      pipelineItemCreationConfig {
        stage {
        overviewFieldsConfig {
          mobileCardOverviewFields
        }
          stageId
          name
          order
          color
          quickEditFields
        }
        activityTemplateId
      }
    }
    ... on ActivityTemplateNotFound {
      message
      activityTemplateId
    }
    ... on ActivityTemplateAccessDenied {
      message
      activityTemplateId
    }
  }
}

template.query:
let selected_row = pipeline_stage_update_permissions_data_table.selectedRow.roleIds
var selected_roles = update_stage_update_permitted_roles.value
var difference = selected_row.filter(x => selected_roles.indexOf(x) === -1);
return difference

var data = GetPipelineStagesBulk.data
return data.getSalesPipelineStages.stages.sort((a, b) => parseFloat(a.order) - parseFloat(b.order));

      gofId

                minValue

              salesTemplateId
              systemFieldEnum

            ... on LongTextField {

              placeholderText
              isDependent
              longTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
              salesTemplateId

                options
              }
            }
            ... on PlainTextField {

      message
      pipelineId

    ... on PipelineTemplates {
      pipelineId
      name

        pipelineItemTemplateId
        name
        pipelineId
        orderedGofIds
        gofs {
          gofId
          name
          description
          orderedFieldIds
          fields {
            __typename
            ... on IntegerField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              numberRangeConfig: rangeConfig {
                minValue

              salesTemplateId

mutation CreateActivityTemplateGof($inputArguments: CreateActivityTemplateGoFParams!) {
  createActivityTemplateGof(params: $inputArguments) {
    __typename
    ... on GoF {
      gofId
      name
      description
      category
      orderedFieldIds
      fields {
      __typename
            ... on IntegerField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId

              fieldType
              isRequired

                minValue
                maxValue

            ... on EmailField {

              gofId

              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent

            ... on FileUploaderField {
              fieldId

              gofId

              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              allowedFormats
              isUnique
              fileUploaderDefaultValue: defaultValue

            ... on LongTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name

              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText

              longTextDefaultValue: defaultValue

            ... on PlainTextField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              plainTextDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on URLField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              regexErrorMessage
              validationRegex
              isUnique
              urlDefaultValue: defaultValue
            }
            ... on TimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              timeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              timerelativeDefaultValue: relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfSeconds
              }
            }
            ... on DateField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              dateDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                valueEnum
                operator
                noOfDays
              }
            }
            ... on DateTimeField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              dateTimeDefaultValue: defaultValue
              relativeDefaultValueConfig {
                dateConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfDays
                }
                timeConfig {
                  valueEnum
                  operator
                  noOfSeconds
                }
              }
            }
            ... on DropdownField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
            }
            ... on MultiSelectField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
            }
            ... on CheckboxGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValues
            }
            ... on RadioGroupField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
            }
            ... on PhoneNumberField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              isUnique
            }
            ... on FieldsSelectorField {
              fieldId
              permissionType
              gofId
              name
              description
              fieldType
              isRequired
              helpText
              tooltip
              placeholderText
              isDependent
              options
              defaultValue
              dependentFields {
                option
                dependentFieldIds
              }
            }    
      }
    }
    ... on ActivityTemplateNotFound {
      message
      activityTemplateId
    }
    ... on GoFNameAlreadyExists {
      message
      name
    }
    ... on UserIsNotAnAdministrator {
      message
    }
  }
